654
01:02:54,665 --> 01:02:58,390
So I could see if somebody identified as having a disability.

655
01:02:58,810 --> 01:03:01,812
And that allowed me to be able to flag and go back.

656
01:03:02,312 --> 01:03:09,077
But I would even say one step further, if you identify as having a disability, you click there.

657
01:03:09,537 --> 01:03:18,783
