658
01:03:19,283 --> 01:03:25,988
Because the disability that I might have and the support need that I might have could be different from someone else's.

659
01:03:26,548 --> 01:03:41,724
And I, you know, and I recall an area office had gone ahead, and I told them that they were going to have to put a halt right on the interviews, because I had a person that was deaf and hard of hearing.

660
01:03:43,004 --> 01:03:45,145
And they asked how long would they have to wait.

661
01:03:45,165 --> 01:03:49,987
